<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>yes24</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN"
      crossorigin="anonymous" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav style="margin-top: 15vh" class="container">
      <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-fill">
        <li
          class="nav-item"
          style="
            border-radius: 0;
            border: 1px solid black;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #999;
          ">
          <a
            id="all"
            class="nav-link"
            onclick="clickCategory(all)"
            aria-current="page"
            href="/list/all"
            style="color: black"
            >종합</a
          >
        </li>
        <li
          class="nav-item"
          style="
            border-radius: 0;
            border: 1px solid black;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #999;
          ">
          <a
            class="nav-link"
            aria-current="page"
            href="/list/realtime"
            style="color: black"
            >실시간</a
          >
        </li>
        <li
          class="nav-item"
          style="
            border-radius: 0;
            border: 1px solid black;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #999;
          ">
          <a
            class="nav-link"
            style="color: black"
            aria-current="page"
            href="/list/day"
            >일별</a
          >
        </li>
        <li
          class="nav-item"
          style="
            border-radius: 0;
            border: 1px solid black;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #999;
          ">
          <a
            class="nav-link"
            style="color: black"
            aria-current="page"
            href="/list/month"
            >월별/주별</a
          >
        </li>
        <li
          class="nav-item"
          style="
            border-radius: 0;
            border: 1px solid black;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #999;
          ">
          <a
            class="nav-link"
            style="color: black"
            aria-current="page"
            href="/list/sale"
            >특가</a
          >
        </li>
        <li
          class="nav-item"
          style="
            border-radius: 0;
            border: 1px solid black;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: #999;
          ">
          <a
            class="nav-link"
            style="color: black"
            aria-current="page"
            href="/list/steady"
            >스테디셀러</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <main style="margin-top: 15px" class="container">
      <h2><%= title %> 베스트</h2>
      <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column">
        <div
          class="cart-box"
          style="
            border: 1px solid black;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
          ">
          <span
            >최근 7일간 온라인과 매장에서의 판매량 및 주문 수를 기준으로 매일
            1회 집계됩니다.</span
          >
          <div class="cart-btns" style="display: flex">
            <button style="margin: 0 10px">전체선택</button>
            <button style="margin: 0 10px">카트에 넣기</button>
            <button style="margin: 0 10px">리스트에 넣기</button>
            <button style="margin: 0 10px">엑셀로 받기</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          style="
            border: 1px solid black;
            margin-top: 10px;
            background: lightgrey;
          ">
          <h4>2023.10.03 ~ 2023.10.09 기준</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% list.forEach((v,i)=>{ %>
      <div
        class="row"
        style="
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          border-bottom: 1px solid black;
        ">
        <h2 class="col-md-1"><%= i+1 %></h2>
        <img
          class="col-md-2"
          style="width: 100px; height: 100px"
          src="<%= v.url %>"
          alt="" />
        <div class="explain col-md-7">
          <p style="font-size: 1.4rem">[도서]<%= v.title %></p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: lightgrey">
            <em>저자</em>/<em>출판사</em>/<em>출판일</em>
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong style="font-size: 1.2rem"> <%= v.price %> </strong>
            <small>원</small>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="btn-box col-md-2"
          style="display: flex; flex-direction: column">
          <button>카트에 넣기</button>
          <button>바로 넣기</button>
          <button>리스트에 넣기</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% }) %>
    </main>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL"
      crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script></script>
  </body>
</html>
